PROGRESSION_STRATEGY:
* Balance multiple paths: combat, trading, exploration, diplomacy
* Team up: Many ranks require teamwork and leadership
* Explore widely: Sector exploration counts toward many ranks
* Build infrastructure: Planet and port ownership provides permanent assets
* Master quantum trading: Advanced ranks heavily reward quantum mastery
* Maintain faction relations: Good standing opens many doors
* Think long-term: Highest ranks are rare multi-year achievements

CONSTRAINTS:
* Ranks never lost once earned
* Requirements cumulative (must meet all criteria)
* Visible to all players (public achievement)
* Some ranks require team leadership or membership
* Fleet Admiral extremely rare by design (<0.01% expected)
* Trading bonuses apply to all port transactions
* Diplomatic immunity only in allied faction territories
* Governance roles require sustained activity and reputation

